Package datastructures.graph

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdjMatrixEdgeWeightedDigraph
    The AdjMatrixEdgeWeightedDigraph class represents a edge-weighted digraph of vertices named 0 through V - 1, where each directed edge is of type DirectedWeightedEdge and has a real-valued weight.
    Digraph
    The Digraph class represents a directed graph of vertices named 0 through V - 1.
    DirectedWeightedEdge
    The DirectedEdge class represents a weighted edge in an EdgeWeightedDigraph.
    DirectedWeightedPath  
    EdgeWeightedDigraph
    The EdgeWeightedDigraph class represents a edge-weighted digraph of vertices named 0 through V - 1, where each directed edge is of type DirectedWeightedEdge and has a real-valued weight.
    EdgeWeightedGraph
    The EdgeWeightedGraph class represents an edge-weighted graph of vertices named 0 through V – 1, where each undirected edge is of type WeightedEdge and has a real-valued weight.
    Graph
    The Graph class represents an undirected graph of vertices named 0 through V – 1.
    VariableEdgeWeightedDigraph
    The VariableEdgeWeightedDigraph class represents a variable/mutable edge-weighted digraph of vertices named 0 through V - 1, where each directed edge is of type DirectedWeightedEdge and has a real-valued weight.
    VariableWeightedGraph
    The VariableEdgeWeightedGraph class represents a variable/mutable edge-weighted graph of vertices named 0 through V - 1, where each undirected edge is of type WeightedEdge and has a real-valued weight.
    WeightedEdge
    The Edge class represents a weighted edge in an EdgeWeightedGraph.
    WeightedPath
